longBusinessSummary: Verisante Technology Inc. does not have significant operations. Previously, it was involved in the design and manufacture of innovative cancer diagnostic devices. The company was formerly known as T-Ray Science Inc. and changed its name to Verisante Technology Inc. in January 2011. Verisante Technology Inc. was incorporated in 2006 and is based in Vancouver, Canada.
